parameters.functionCode: return [{ json: { query: 'qual e a melhor forma de pagamento' } }];

parameters.query:
SELECT
  id,
  title,
  content,
  ts_rank_cd(
    tsv_content,
    websearch_to_tsquery('portuguese', '{{ $json["query"] }}')
  ) AS score_bm25
FROM documents
WHERE
  tsv_content @@ websearch_to_tsquery('portuguese', '{{ $json["query"] }}')
ORDER BY score_bm25 DESC
LIMIT 5;

SELECT
    id,
    title,
    content,
    1 - (embedding <=> '{{ $json["embeddings"] ? '[' + $json["embeddings"].join(",") + ']' : '[]' }}'::vector) AS similarity
FROM
    documents
ORDER BY
    similarity DESC
LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, title, content, hybrid_search_score($1::vector, embedding, $2::text, content) AS score FROM documents ORDER BY score DESC LIMIT 5;
